<option>Veetaal - Shadow Knight - 12</option>
</select></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthedruidsgrove.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=rtfm>rtfm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/7/01 9:10:12 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What's wth snare?</span><hr size=1> Ensnare? <br>
<br>
